{"about_the_game":"Tri-Star is a an endless horizontal-scrolling space shooter featuring Roguelike and Roguelite elements. Blast your way through waves of tricky enemies to face off against arduous boss battles. Form a squadron of three unique ships from an expanding roster and kit them out with upgrades as you engage in a battle for survival. Defeat bosses and achieve high scores to unlock a large pool of new enhancements, game modes and ships to try on your next playthrough.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755600/extras/TriStar_Features.gif?t=1637697717\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Squadrons: Select three ships and manage their loadout as you attempt to get as far as you can. Leave damaged ships at base to be repaired while you continue the fight </li><li>12 Playable Ships: Each with its own primary and special weapons </li><li>Custom Loadout: Use the scrap of your fallen enemies to enhance 6 different stats and attach over 60 varied upgrades </li><li>Endless Replayability: Play again and again through mostly randomly generated levels </li><li>Score Attack: Short on time? Go solo with no repairs or upgrades and amass as high of a score as you can </li><li>Ace Mode: Prove you have what it takes to take on fiercer enemies who will show no mercy</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"My Ship is Unbending","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755600/761bbcc1f5473e2ff5e0c82e85973501de874ed9.jpg"},{"name":"One Shot is all I Need","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755600/1c661fa5231bc806869c7022755e5cddd4c62995.jpg"},{"name":"Now With More Pew Pew","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755600/94e77b06a7a371ddcfb275c6623053e1bef2b98a.jpg"},{"name":"Unleash the power of the Sun","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1755600/f545e8e